Day 957. "I do not feel obliged to believe that the same God who has endowed us with sense, reason, and intellect has intended us to forgo their use," so says Galileo, the Father of Modern Science, who was an astronomer, physicist, engineer, philosopher, mathematician in the 1600s. Whew! He obviously had A LOT on his mind... as did this actor, doing the work of portraying Galileo at a Renaissance Fair. THINKINiG fills us up. And CRITICAL thinking is essential for a rational and democratic society that wisely works for the 'greater good'. Perhaps we should follow the lead of the Wizard-of-Oz-Scarecrow, who felt empty without a brain and BEWARE "...the dangerousness of a hollow man." (David Brooks, contemporary columnist for The New York Times.) #thinking #thought #brainscience #galileo #acting #actor #sense #reason #greatergood #illustrator #fineartist #storyteller #sketchoftheday #lasermodemasters

And it was
When I looked
Back
At it all,
Back at
Every inch
Of this 
Human 
Existence,
That every
Wrong decision,
Every ounce 
Of pain and bitterness
That I had held onto
With such vigor,
Such rage
Deep within
My bones --
I realized that
All of that
Heartache 
Meant
Absolutely nothing.
In fact, 
All I saw when 
I looked back
Was beauty,
And I was in 
Awe
That the hurt
I had once
Felt so
Intensely,
So deeply
At the center
Of my core
Was able to 
Morph
Into something
So elegant and true
To me.
I saw the 
Entirety 
Of myself
And it was 
Nothing
Short of
Stunning
To witness.
Hopefully,
When you gain
The courage
To look back
At your 
Follies,
You'll be greeted 
With the same
Warmth.

My #ThoughtOfTheDay today is - Failure. Why are we scared of it and why do we strive for perfection all the time?🤔

This video is of me being a hot mess in @ashton_sands_ldn class. To be perfectly honest, I'm a hot mess in 90% of the dance classes I do.. but if I didn't challenge myself and FAIL Id never get better. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Today's #throwbackTuesday is not a picture but rather a thought. A thought of the years I was unhappy with my body. Unsatisfied with how I looked and actually really hard on myself. .... today I treat it differently. 
Your body is a pretty amazing thing. As soon as you start treating it as amazing, you'll both start to believe it! #tuesdaythought

“Measure your S U C C E S S only by what matters to you. Your H A P P I N E S S, and the happiness you bring to others“ 💭
.
.
One of my happiest moments is 4000m high, at the top of the mountain, as there is something quite magical about this space. The blistering sun, on a clear blue skied day. The calming inner thoughts of your mind, when your headphones are blasting some heavy metal. Find your happy moments, and capture them how you can reflect best; photos, videos, a grain of sand from the beach, or a pebble from the mountain you hiked. Whatever it takes to hold on to these moments, the pro-longed benefits of holding on outweighs any current negative thoughts ... ⛷🎿❄️
.

Heute mal ein etwas ernsteres Thema (eigentlich find ich gehört sowas für mich nicht so auf Instagram aber ich wollte mal mit euch darüber reden). Hier ein Bild von mir.. nach außen sieht alles oft immer so toll aus nur innerlich geht es mir zurzeit leider nicht so gut. Ich leide an sehr vielen Selbstzweifeln und das liegt daran, dass ich mich in meinem Körper derzeit nicht wohl fühle. Ich lese hier zurzeit sehr viel über #bodyshaming , dass man sich doch in seinem Körper wohl fühlen soll ihn nehmen soll wie er ist etc. Aber so fühl ich mich einfach nicht wohl. Das merke ich erst recht bei dem warmen Wetter: man sieht den Bauch mehr, dicke Oberschenkel und Waden ich trau mich nicht sommerlich rauszugehen etc. Daher mache ich nun derzeit viel Sport die Woche und gehe jeden Tag eine kleine! runde joggen damit ich hoffentlich bis zum Juli noch etwas abspecken kann. Das Gefühl bleibt jedoch: sobald ich was esse nehme ich gefühlt zu obwohl es gesund ist.. vllt kennt jemand von euch diese Gedanken und Sorgen ja und kann mir vllt ein paar Tipps geben wie ihr damit umgeht und vllt auch mit ein paar Kilos mehr im Sommer was ihr da macht etc? Das wäre so lieb 💕
